OL,6,FA driver who killed his wife in a
OL,7,Fcrash after running late for work has
OL,8,Fbeen jailed.
OL,10,FAsen Kurtev had 39-year-old Sofka
OL,11,FMitkova and three other colleagues in
OL,12,Fhis Vauxhall Zafira when he caused a
OL,13,Fhead-on collision on the A16 near
OL,14,FSpalding, Lincolnshire, on 4 March
OL,15,Flast year.
OL,17,FHis wife, who was the front seat
OL,18,Fpassenger, suffered fatal injuries.
OL,19,FThe other passengers were seriously
OL,20,Finjured, along with the driver of the
OL,21,Fother car, a Volkswagen Scirocco.
