OL,3,CDriver running late for work killed
OL,4,Cwife in crash
OL,6,FKurtev, 46, of Carlton Road, Boston,
OL,7,Fadmitted causing death by dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving and serious injury by
OL,9,Fdangerous driving.
OL,11,FHe was jailed for 10 years and nine
OL,12,Fmonths.
OL,14,FLincoln Crown Court heard he had
OL,15,Falready overtaken other vehicles
OL,16,Fbefore he attempted an overtaking
OL,17,Fmanoeuvre when the crash happened at
OL,18,Fabout 6.50am.
OL,20,FWitnesses said he had been driving
OL,21,Ferratically in heavy traffic.
