OL,3,CDriver running late for work killed
OL,4,Cwife in crash
OL,6,FKurtev told police he had been in a
OL,7,Frush as he and his passengers were
OL,8,Flate for work.
OL,10,FDet Sgt Adam Doona, of Lincolnshire
OL,11,FPolice, said: "Kurtev's lateness for
OL,12,Fwork led to him driving dangerously,
OL,13,Fcarrying out inappropriate overtakes
OL,14,Fwith a reckless regard for the safety
OL,15,Fof other road users.
OL,17,F"As a result, his wife paid the
OL,18,Fultimate price and four other
OL,19,Findividuals sustained serious injuries
OL,20,Fwhich required extensive ongoing
OL,21,Ftreatment.
