OL,6,F"Whilst no-one wants to be late, it is
OL,7,Fbetter to arrive late, than not at
OL,8,Fall. The selfish actions and utter
OL,9,Fdisregard for others that Kurtev
OL,10,Fdisplayed have rightly attracted a
OL,11,Fsubstantial sentence from the court."
OL,13,FKurtev was also banned from driving
OL,14,Ffor 12 years two months.
